{"tid":1631483,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［鶳］未FC, 藍護士強行帶被捕受傷義士去落口供","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:38:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T01:42:12.000Z","uid":272569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4aee2729c81f72f54aedd0c0b6f859535e420c01","tid":1631483,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:38:04.000Z","msg":"下面三隻強行帶被捕受傷義士去落口供<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">未FC</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如真，除左鶳之外要去醫管局投訴<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nzRcHzJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnzRcHzJ.png&h=a605985d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a13b1f66df706582a7a4d62eaa2c8fd5fe9585ae","tid":1631483,"uid":75959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:40:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">大家 呢幾日都係行動日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但連登都無比大陸DDos攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就證明左係大量五毛做緊野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又分化又風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地係時候要醒下<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰<br />\n<br />\n跟住就係開始做正經野：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 推紅色的士撞人單野<br />\n<br />\n2.推黑警又當街踢人單野<br />\n<br />\n3.九龍塘軍營入面有綠色防暴警既片<br />\n<br />\n4.解釋返裝修既原因比外國知<br />\n<br />\n5.宣傳黑紅藍黃既概念<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地唔好再比五毛搞爆連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"ae3d6016b7517060bc9c938e15bbdf01fa2d77